      &lt;h4&gt;2. Andrew Grojean&lt;/h4&gt;
      &lt;br&gt;
              &lt;a href="http://mashable.com/2011/09/30/facebook-timeline-cover-photos/#278812-Andrew-Grojean"&gt;&lt;img width="400" style="border:none" title="2. Andrew Grojean" src="http://6.mshcdn.com/wp-content/gallery/facebook-gallery/andrew.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a cunning way to keep the old Facebook design.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;      &lt;br&gt;
