      &lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Maggie is mixing up her social networks with a Facebook / Google+ profile.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;      &lt;br&gt;
      &lt;h4&gt;10. Ekkapong Techawongthaworn &lt;/h4&gt;
      &lt;br&gt;
              &lt;a href="http://mashable.com/2011/09/30/facebook-timeline-cover-photos/#2789510-Ekkapong-Techawongthaworn"&gt;&lt;img width="400" style="border:none" title="10. Ekkapong Techawongthaworn " src="http://7.mshcdn.com/wp-content/gallery/facebook-gallery/ekkapong.jpg"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The low placement of the profile pic box doesn't necessarily lend itself to a full body shot, but Ekkapong found a good way to work around that.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
