 page layout before anyone else, but if you're really into it then hit up TechCrunch for the full instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://techcrunch.com/2011/09/22/how-to-enable-facebook-timeline/"&gt;How To Enable Facebook Timeline Right This Second&lt;/a&gt; | TechCrunch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
